title: Living Game Volume 1-10
description: A romantic comedy about a Fuwa, a guy living in a small apartment in overcrowded Tokyo, who wants to have a place of his own. Because of a building accident in their new office building, Fuwa&#039;s company (5 employees) had to move into his apartment, right after he had moved to a larger place. And the new employee (Hiyama Izumi, a 15 year-old girl) had to move into Fuwa&#039;s place, as she had just come from the country. Then Fuwa&#039;s old girlfriend Tokiko, who had already gotten married, ran away from her husband and came to Fuwa&#039;s place.
